# This is second day of 100 days of code challenge.
# Que.=> Build a calculator which can split bills along with tip between n number of people.
# Solve:-
bill_amount = float(input('What is the bill amount? '))
split_among = int(input('Split among how peaple? '))
tip = float(input('What is tip percentage? '))
individual_pay = (bill_amount / split_among) * ((tip / 100) + 1)
print (round(individual_pay,2))
